  "text": "Then, the zeros of φ(z), which are referred to the spectral zeros of f (z), need to be assigned at given locations. This interpolation problem is of interest in spectrum analysis applications [CITATION_1] . This is also of interest if one wants to parameterize all the solutions via spectral zeros.",
